[{"location":"Risk_Functions/#Risk-Functions","page":"API","title":"Risk Functions","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"Risk_Functions/","page":"API","title":"API","text":"port_variance\nport_std\nport_mad","category":"page"},{"location":"Risk_Functions/#PortfolioOptimiser.port_variance","page":"API","title":"PortfolioOptimiser.port_variance","text":"port_variance(w, cov_mtx)\n\nComputes the overall portfolio variance according to the weights w, and covariance matrix cov_mtx.\n\nThe portfolio variance sigma^2, is defined as:\n\nsigma^2 = bmw^T Sigma bmw\n\nwhere sigma is the overall portfolio standard deviation, ^T the transpose operator, w the weights, and Sigma the covariance matrix.\n\n\n\n\n\nport_variance(w::AbstractVector, cov::AbstractMatrix)\n\nCompute the variance of a portfolio with weights w and covariance cov. Square of port_std.\n\nmathrmvar(bmx mathbfSigma) = bmx^intercal mathbfSigma bmx\n\nwhere bmx are the weights and mathbfSigma the covariance matrix.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"Risk_Functions/#PortfolioOptimiser.port_std","page":"API","title":"PortfolioOptimiser.port_std","text":"port_std(w::AbstractVector, cov::AbstractMatrix)\n\nCompute the standard deviation of a portfolio with weights w and covariance cov. Square root of port_variance.\n\nmathrmstd(bmx mathbfSigma) = sqrtbmx^intercal mathbfSigma bmx\n\nwhere bmx are the weights and mathbfSigma the covariance matrix.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"Risk_Functions/#PortfolioOptimiser.port_mad","page":"API","title":"PortfolioOptimiser.port_mad","text":"port_mad(x::AbstractVector)\n\nCompute the mean absolute deviation of a vector x of portfolio returns.\n\nmathrmMAD(bmx) = dfrac1T sumlimits_t=1^T lvert x_t - mathbbE(bmx) rvert\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"idx/#PortfolioOptimiser-API-Index","page":"Index","title":"PortfolioOptimiser API Index","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"idx/","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = PortfolioOptimiser","category":"page"},{"location":"#PortfolioOptimiser","page":"Home","title":"PortfolioOptimiser","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Documentation for PortfolioOptimiser.","category":"page"}]
